urf - wurde sowohl architekturwissenschaftlich, kunsthistorisch und städtebaulich bewertet und interpretiert.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 7aARCHITECTURE / History / Modern (late 19th Century to 1945).2bisacsh1 aCollins, Christiane, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMönninger, Michael, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aSemsroth, Klaus, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts and Architecture 2014z9783110369595oZDB-23-DKA08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Complete Package 2014z9783110369526oZDB-23-DGG40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783205793205423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783205793205.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2014  aZDB-23-DKAb2014